search:
| rest splunk_server=usrlsplnkidx013 /services/server/info
| fields splunk_server version
| join type=outer splunk_server [rest splunk_server=usrlsplnkidx013 /services/server/status/installed-file-integrity
    | fields splunk_server check_ready check_failures.fail]
| eval check_status = case(isnull('check_failures.fail') AND isnotnull(check_ready), "enabled", 'check_failures.fail' == "check_disabled", "disabled", isnull(check_ready), "feature unavailable")
| eval check_ready = if(check_status == "enabled", check_ready, "N/A")
| fields version check_status check_ready
| rename version AS "Splunk version" check_status AS "Check status" check_ready AS "Results ready?"

| rest splunk_server=usrlsplnkidx013 /services/server/status/installed-file-integrity 
| fields check_failures.* 
| untable splunk_server file_path check_result 
| replace "check_failures.*" WITH "*" IN file_path
| fields file_path check_result
| rename file_path AS "File path" check_result AS "Check result"
search index=_internal "block"  NOT "search_id=remote_usrlsplunksh006"  NOT INFO  NOT "/servicesNS/nobody/Trustar/saved/searches/Trustar"
